with all the other kids.

918
00:58:37,720 --> 00:58:39,995
I thought he was only looking at me.

919
00:58:41,120 --> 00:58:43,714
I was afraid he was going to arrest me.

920
00:58:43,840 --> 00:58:45,876
He had those eyes, and that...

