975
01:02:53,440 --> 01:02:54,589
Lupe...

976
01:02:55,560 --> 01:02:58,120
Can you get me Ben Wetzel up in Austin?

977
01:03:31,840 --> 01:03:33,273
Wetbacks again.

978
01:03:41,440 --> 01:03:42,793
Border Patrol?

979
01:04:42,320 --> 01:04:43,275
Mom?

980
01:04:43,360 --> 01:04:44,349
Yeah.

981
01:04:44,440 --> 01:04:45,919
You staying out here?

982
01:04:46,320 --> 01:04:47,548
For a while.

