What do you think?

985
01:06:28,640 --> 01:06:30,437
Hey, 'morning, sir!

986
01:06:30,520 --> 01:06:32,272
Hey, Pete. How's it going?

987
01:06:32,920 --> 01:06:34,512
Time marches on.

988
01:06:34,680 --> 01:06:35,874
How much you got left?

989
01:06:35,960 --> 01:06:37,359
Three months.

990
01:06:38,520 --> 01:06:42,229
Stop growing that locoweed at your place,
you'd see more daylight.

991
01:06:42,320 --> 01:06:44,709
It was for personal consumption.

992
01:06:45,200 --> 01:06:47,953
You going to smoke an acre and a half
of marijuana?

993
01:06:48,720 --> 01:06:51,712
I got a bad stomach. It helps me to digest.

994
01:06:51,800 --> 01:06:54,075
