1001
01:07:10,840 --> 01:07:13,070
I'm surprised he bothered with it.

1002
01:07:13,160 --> 01:07:15,276
He was afraid I'd poison somebody.

1003
01:07:17,320 --> 01:07:19,629
Your father tried to do good for people.

1004
01:07:19,960 --> 01:07:21,712
- So I've heard.
- And your mother...

1005
01:07:21,800 --> 01:07:23,199
...she was a saint.

1006
01:07:23,800 --> 01:07:26,268
Remember that summer I built that patio
at your house?

1007
01:07:26,360 --> 01:07:28,555
